                <p>Partially preserved. A cross with arrays in the angles marks the beginning and probably the end of the text.The inscription is from the Treatise of Evagrius Ponticus "Περὶ τῶν οκτῶ πνευμάτων τῆς πονηρίας" ("De octo spiritibus malitiae" / "The Eight Spirits of Wickedness"/ "Eight Thoughts") (PG 77, 1145, l.8-9)</p>
